🚨 Raksha Saheli – AI Safety Companion

🌟 Project Overview

Raksha Saheli is a smart safety web application designed to provide instant emergency support for:

- 👧 Children
- 👩 Women
- 🚑 Accident victims

It helps users quickly contact emergency services, share live location, and access nearby police stations.

---

🚀 Features

🔹 Role-Based Safety Modes

- Child Safety Mode (1098)
- Women Safety Mode (1091)
- Accident Emergency Mode (108)

🔹 SOS Emergency Button

- Instant emergency call
- Loud alarm sound
- Vibrations
- Sends alert to backend server

🔹 📍 Live Location Sharing

- Sends Google Maps link via WhatsApp

🔹 🚔 Nearby Police Stations

- Uses location to find nearby police stations
- Direct map navigation

🔹 🌐 Universal SOS Link

- Share SOS link with anyone instantly

